{"type":"message","id":"eecc4c48","parentId":"8d7e7eb9","timestamp":"2026-03-26T03:56:18.822Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the answer! The API response tells us that the current app is **missing edit permission** for the wiki space. The error message is:\n\"permission denied: wiki space permission denied, tenant needs edit permission.\"\n\nSo the issue is that the Feishu app needs to be granted edit permission to the wiki space `7615846908665285857`. The user needs to go to the Feishu admin panel and add this app to the wiki space with edit permissions.","thinkingSignature":"99dda26f1c8978af91e161ffdbac1825243c41dc7143fd8d22c592108659f480"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]]\n\n权限测试结果出来了：\n\n**❌ 当前缺少写入权限**\n\n错误信息：\n> `permission denied: wiki space permission denied, tenant needs edit permission.`\n\n**问题原因：**\n飞书应用（`cli_a93a5bdf09625cd2`）还没有被授权编辑知识库 **AI知识库** (space_id: `7615846908665285857`)\n\n**解决方法：**\n需要管理员在飞书管理后台 → **知识库** → 找到 **AI知识库** → **权限设置** → 添加该应用并授予**编辑权限**。\n\n添加后再试一次就好了 🦐"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5-highspeed","usage":{"input":16054,"output":235,"cacheRead":12885,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29174,"cost":{"input":0.0096324,"output":0.0005639999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0007731,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0109695}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774497374068}}
